milestones.description: Aftab Ahmed and Mushfiqur's 132-run partnership is BAN's highest for the 3rd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 128 between Rajin Saleh and Alok Kapali
Chigumbura has broken the record for most sixes in an innings (7) in ODIs for ZIM, going past Dave Houghton's 6
